node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'I Made Some Mistakes I Cant Change, But I Changed So I Wont Make The Same Mistakes!!'.

node.text: Stop living in shame and forgive yourself and let it go! If you erased all your mistakes you wouldn’t be the amazing human you are today! Life is about change! God has You! Grow through what you’re going through! Cheers to a better Us!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'When God shows you something about someone, don't dismiss 1t. It's clarity you PRAYED for, not confusion!'.

node.text: When God shows you something about someone, don’t dismiss it. It’s clarity you PRAYED for, not confusion! #realtalkkim

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on August 14, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'CATFESH RELATIONSHIPS SERIES 3NINO CHN'T WAIT TO IN & Sa SEE YOU! SUNDAYS 10:00AM 11:30AM'.

node.text: Sunday’s at @mylimitlesschurch are the best!!!! We can’t wait to see you! Beat us there! #limitlessnation

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'You're in bed right now worrying how to deal with a a situation that seems out of your hands. God says; "Be still, I'm already at work. Trust Me and rest." Amen.'.
Photo by REAL TALK KIM on August 13, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'YOU cannot have clowns around you and not expect your life to be a circus. @REALTALKKIM'.

node.text: MARRY someone who will not only accept the call of God on your life, but will also help you fulfill it and not try to kill it. The wrong person can delay your destiny! Listen, nothing worse than marrying Satan and having to pretend you are happy! Stop that!! Wait on God! #single #relationship #dating

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'God is moving on your behalf today... He will visit your home this weekend with miracles and answers. www.realtalkkim.com'.

node.text:
God is going to take you from HAVING the dream to LIVING it. 
 “Trust in the Lord with all your heart, And lean not on your own understanding; In all your ways acknowledge Him, And He shall direct your paths.”
Proverbs 3:5-6 NKJV

node.text: I got to have a fun day with this amazing Jesus loving crew! We all will be dropping it for Jesus tonight at 7PM. See you soon Myrtle Beach!

node.text:
Good Mornin Family!! 
Today I decree that you experience restoration from the years the locusts and cankerworm have eaten. I decree everything that has seemed to have decayed or crumbled be reestablished into newness and may you begin to flourish again. I prophesy a rebuilding of the old waste places and that streams begin to flow in the desert. I break the power of distraction, attack, and devastation in Jesus name. I pray that you begin to receive restitution, payback, benefits, and reimbursements. 
I pray that fruitfulness will remain in your life and that you will experience fulfillment, success, and complete contentment. I prophecy that all that God has planned for your life will begin to fully manifest in this season before you! I speak all of this in Jesus name. #realtalk #realtalkkim

Photo by REAL TALK KIM on August 12, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'REMINDER Your self worth is not defined by the way others treat you! @REALTALKKIM'.

node.text:
God validates you! He approves of you! Their opinions didn’t make you and won’t break you. Stay focused! Have I not commanded you? Be strong and courageous. Do not be afraid; do not be discouraged, for the Lord your God will be with you wherever you go. Joshua 1:9

When you don’t feel like you’re good enough, it’s easy to want to blend in, hide in the back, and avoid bringing any attention to yourself. But God commands you to be strong and courageous!

Not in your own abilities or strengths, but because God will be with you wherever you go. You can live in confidence because of His strength. #realtalkkim
